2. NAT
✅ Full Form

NAT = Network Address Translation

✅ What is NAT?

NAT allows private servers to access the internet without being publicly exposed.

🧠 Problem Without NAT

Private subnet servers:

Cannot download updates
Cannot call external APIs
Cannot install packages

Because:

❌ No internet access.

✅ Solution → NAT Gateway
Private EC2 → NAT Gateway → Internet

✔ Outgoing internet allowed
❌ Incoming internet blocked

✅ Why Developers Use NAT

Example:

Spring Boot server needs:

Maven dependencies
Payment API calls
Email services

But should NOT be publicly accessible.

👉 NAT solves this.

🔐 Security Benefit
Backend hidden from internet
Only outbound communication allowed
